channel.title: Its time for me to go
channel.description:
Hey guys, most of you remember me. Its finally time for me to leave Mopar. Even though this is my first time back on Mopar in months. I now have to move on, working 2 jobs, and starting to drive now. Mopar has given me many experiences and opportunities to succeed, in life, and in gaming. I remember when i first started here i didnt know 1 thing. Even though i forgot half the shit i learned here ( Coding, Java, ETC. ), im still thankful for this opportunity. I will visit here every now and then, to meet back with some of my old friends here.
Thanks to everyone for this amazing experience.
(N)eon
